author: Bianca Giulione
title: Azealia Banks Has Been Issued an Arrest Warrant
text:
Ooops! Rapper Azealia Bank s skipped out on a very important court appearance in New York yesterday. She failed to show up in Manhattan Criminal Court Monday, March 6, allegedly playing hooky to attend Paris Fashion Week. According to a statement by her entertainment lawyer, “Azealia Banks mistakenly believed she had a court appearance on March 8th instead of March 6th.” The hearing is related to a 2015 incident at a New York nightclub where she was accused of attacking a female security guard.
"Knock knock its the police we have an arrest warrant out for you ms banks"
Azealia Banks: pic.twitter.com/OIujkBiahK 
— trent (@trentlilweezy) March 7, 2017 

Banks has been a rather controversial figure in recent rap history. She beefed with Rihanna on Instagram over the Muslim Ban a couple months back, has apparently been sacrificing chickens for witchcraft purposes in her closet, and can’t seem to lock down a manager. But there’s no denying she makes dope tracks – we hope Zeze will get this all sorted so she can lay some more bars down in the studio soon.
Azealia Banks dropped “Crown” produced by Lunice last month. Listen to it below.
